.SH FILES
.BR nicy " reads the following configuration files from "
.IR $XDG_CONFIG_HOME " (when not run by superuser), "  /etc ", and " \
/usr/local/etc " per order of precedence."
.P
.I nicy/environment
.RS
Environment file. See ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES.
.P
.RE
.I nicy/*.cgroups
.RS
Cgroups files. See CONFIGURATION.
.P
.RE
.I nicy/*.types
.RS
Types files. See CONFIGURATION.
.P
.RE
.I nicy/rules.d/*.rules
.RS
Rules files. See CONFIGURATION.
